OL,3,CBorders arts festival confirmed for
OL,4,Ctwo more years thanks to funding grant
OL,6,FDunsPlayFest, the annual arts festival
OL,7,Fin the Scottish Borders has been
OL,8,Fawarded #100,000 by Creative Scotland
OL,9,Fto host the event for the next two
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FOrganisers say that the funding
OL,13,Fprovides a secure foundation on which
OL,14,Fto build the 2025 and 2026 festivals
OL,15,Fand will mean they can invest in
OL,16,Fbringing professional performing arts
OL,17,Fevents to a bigger audience in Duns.
