OL,3,CBorders arts festival confirmed for
OL,4,Ctwo more years thanks to funding grant
OL,6,FDunsPlayFest was established in 2019
OL,7,Fby Director John McEwen and a group of
OL,8,Flocal volunteers. It aims to provide a
OL,9,Fshowcase for new theatre, new writing
OL,10,Fand new talent from the Borders and
OL,11,Fbeyond.
OL,13,FRecent festival programmes have
OL,14,Fincluded an offering of over 60
OL,15,Fperforming arts events, including
OL,16,Fmusic, dance and spoken word
OL,17,Fperformances, creative writing and
OL,18,Ftheatre technical skills workshops, a
OL,19,Fcreative writing programme with local
OL,20,Fschools and a Family Arts Day held in
OL,21,Fthe grounds of Duns Castle.
