OL,3,CBorders arts festival confirmed for
OL,4,Ctwo more years thanks to funding grant
OL,6,FDirector John McEwen said: "We are
OL,7,Fimmensely grateful to Creative
OL,8,FScotland whose first grant to us of
OL,9,F#10,000 back in 2019, helped us to
OL,10,Fshape our vision of what has since
OL,11,Fbecome a solid and successful annual,
OL,12,Fnine-day festival of new drama: a
OL,13,Fwhole-hearted celebration of community
OL,14,Fand creativity.
