OL,3,CBorders arts festival confirmed for
OL,4,Ctwo more years thanks to funding grant
OL,6,FThat the small market town of Duns,
OL,7,Fnestled in the heart of Berwickshire,
OL,8,Fa county with no professional theatre,
OL,9,Fshould play host to what is now
OL,10,Frecognised as a major event in the
OL,11,FScottish theatrical year, is almost
OL,12,Fbreathtaking.
OL,14,FLorna Duguid, Multi-Artform Manager at
OL,15,FCreative Scotland said: "The growth of
OL,16,FDunsPlayFest over the last five years
OL,17,Fis testament to the passion and
OL,18,Fefforts of everyone involved in the
OL,19,Ffestival.
